# These are NOT secret (they're public in your APK anyway)
# but listed here for documentation:
#
#   AdMob App ID:        ca-app-pub-8244046288565559~XXXXXXXXXX
#   Banner Ad Unit:      ca-app-pub-8244046288565559/XXXXXXXXXX
