# ── Quick Setup for a New Machine ───────────────────────────
#
# 1. Clone the repo
# 2. Create android/key.properties (see section 1 above)
# 3. Copy gkquiz-release.jks to android/app/
# 4. Copy service-account.json to:
#      C:\Users\<you>\.config\google-play-developer-mcp\
# 5. Run: flutter pub get
# 6. Run: flutter build appbundle --release
#
# To deploy: node AI/deploy_to_play.mjs
